gw.api.print

Class PrintTemplateParameterSet

  • java.lang.Object
    • gw.api.print.PrintTemplateParameterSet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Iterable<PrintTemplateParameter>

    public class PrintTemplateParameterSet
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<PrintTemplateParameter>
    A set of PrintTemplateParameter objects for a print template. A parameter set can only have one parameter with a given id; if more than one parameter with a given id is added then only the last add will be remembered.
